text: The Salt Lake Tabernacle is a building in Temple Square in Salt Lake City, Utah. It was built by The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints (LDS Church) in 1867., See paragraph 3 ==References== Category:Mormonism Category:Churches in the United States Category:Buildings and structures in Utah Category:Salt Lake City Category:1867 establishments in the United States Category:19th-century establishments in Utah
